title.narrative: Building Alliance for Local Advancement, Development and Investment Capacity Building (BALADI CAP)

description.narrative: (Lebanon): With FY 2019 resources, the Building Alliances for Local.Advancement, Development, and Investment - Capacity Building (BALADI CAP).activity will continue to provide tailored capacity development assistance and.small grants to local Civil Society Organizations (CSOs). This includes.supporting 1) a new cohort of faith-based, non-governmental organizations to.provide basic essential services to religious and ethnic minorities in.under-served communities, 2) three Intermediary Service Organizations and their.CSO members to further expand their reach and amplify the impact of their.advocacy efforts, and 3) civil society organizations to increase transparency and to combat corruption by providing much-needed technical knowledge and expertise on public procurement and other government oversight issues. BALADI CAP will leverage its well-established Good Governance and Accountability Advocacy Network local CSOs to assist legislators in addressing these issues..
